==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Maybe
<hw>May"be</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <ety>[For <ets>it may
be</ets>.]</ety> <def>Perhaps; possibly; peradventure.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Maybe</qex> the amorous count solicits her.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>In a liberal and, <qex>maybe</qex>, somewhat reckless way.</q>
<rj><qau>Tylor.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Maybe</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Maybe
<hw>May"be</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Possible; probable, but not
sure.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Then add those <qex>maybe</qex> years thou hast to live.</q>
<rj><qau>Driden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Maybe</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Maybe
<hw>May"be</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Possibility; uncertainty.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>What they offer is mere <qex>maybe</qex> and shift.</q>
<rj><qau>Creech.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Maybird</ent>⟦br⟧
